data.description: Welcome to this fantastic legal 2-flat located in the vibrant Gage Park neighborhood of Chicago. This property presents an excellent opportunity for both investors and homeowners looking for an income-generating property or a multi-generational living setup. Situated on a well-maintained street, this property boasts a newer roof as of 2021, providing peace of mind and long-term durability. Additionally, a new garage as of March 2022, offering secure parking and storage space for both units. One of the highlights of this property is the low property taxes, which makes it even more attractive for potential buyers. Enjoy the benefits of affordable ownership while taking advantage of the income potential from renting out the second unit. The second unit in this 2-flat duplexes to the attic, creating a spacious and versatile living area. This layout allows for additional bedrooms, a home office, or a recreational space, providing flexibility for different needs and preferences. The property is ready to welcome new occupants. Enjoy the convenience of nearby schools, parks, shops, and restaurants. With easy access to public transportation and major highways, commuting to other parts of Chicago is a breeze. Whether you're an investor seeking a profitable rental property or a homeowner looking for an income-generating home, this legal 2-flat in Gage Park is a remarkable opportunity.  Schedule a showing today and explore the potential this property has to offer.
